Not yet, no. Though I'll say if it's not clear that this is the capital city of Nocten. Still debating on a good name for it...

I'll be honest, most NPC names were made on the fly, heh. Nocterrans generally have names that are taken from Egyptian myth and history, albeit chopped up and scrambled. As a bonus, Caithians are themes after old Fae lore. Toldrum is taken from one tale of the Cait Sith, and Niat is taken from Titania, queen of faeries.
